{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4f82db98a7","title":"中文系一年级是个独裁王国","origin":"《右派言行集(下集)》 (全校学生中部分右派言行)，中共云南大学委员会编，一九五七年九月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"60d217bd36","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"4f82db98a7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"2499a730cb","name":"云南大学"},{"id":"a5de47d9ae","name":"张宗礼"},{"id":"aa14008199","name":"欧阳己"},{"id":"eeb18f2237","name":"王立名"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4face5c5a2","type":"title","text":"中文系一年级是个独裁王国","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"181524e82c","type":"authors","text":"云南大学张宗礼欧阳己王立名","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"78b7fbe43e","type":"subtitle","text":"中一是个独裁王国　　中文系一年级абв(张宗礼)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"2dfd11650b","type":"paragraph","text":"诸君以为中文系一年级风平浪静吗？我们有的是藏之已久的激流！若还不信，马上分解：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"19c481598a","type":"paragraph","text":"一、党团员包打天下","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"0bc551c9d5","type":"paragraph","text":"中一有四个党员，分担了党团支书及班主席，还有武显章同志无事干，本期在排除以群众身份担任副班主席的张蜀雁后，就被安插为学习委员了。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"d464e38c43","type":"paragraph","text":"中一的文武官员都由党支部借班会提名，群众作表决机器而产生，难道我们百分之百的爱戴这些候选人吗？问题是他们只提五名候选人，就要我们选这五名，这样的明码实价的“民选”，我们哪里还敢自打折扣呢？","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"c829147bf4","type":"paragraph","text":"目前为止，一应文武官员仅李国亮、吴忠烈是群众，就这二人也不过是“民主花瓶”而已。如我班向全校挑战事，先由第一小组向班提起，而身为第一小组组长的李国亮就全不知道，其他群众更摸不清头脑。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"bef818aa6f","type":"paragraph","text":"二、排挤异己分子","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"fe8248d5aa","type":"paragraph","text":"上期以群众身份参加班会的张蜀雁、吴忠烈，除吴被“五提——五选——五决”留任外，张则不知何故被挤跑了，是由于他不称职吗？还是张不负责呢？但我们却未听见张有非议，如果说个别人对张有意见，又安知别人对其留任者无意见？如何又不撤换呢？大概因为他是群众，属于“异己”分子是被排除了。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"be6c0b6d1d","type":"paragraph","text":"三、中央集权制","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"fd99391993","type":"paragraph","text":"班上做事情，连某些班委也不知道，就以听周总理报告一事而论，最初悉各班是用推选、拈阄等方式而去，我班则由三位一体的负责人指定。负责长并说：“明知大家不同意，但我们就要这样做。”这是多么蔑视群众力量的独裁表现啊！类似情形如“政委制”的编定宿舍，由三位一体的负责人独干等。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"d954a3aba6","type":"paragraph","text":"四、以教育者自居的人","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"bcec42f65b","type":"paragraph","text":"三位一体的负责人，每四周给大家上一次政治课，名之曰“民主生活”(我们不知其它班是否这样)。实是发表典型“杀鸭子给鹅看”。班上社会活动很多，例如有一周(大约是第九周)，除了星期五，其余五个下午都有社会活动。有个欧阳己同学说了句“绳子架在脖子上”，教育者就大发雷霆。另有一个同学余战生因为牙痛引起脸肿，与同学无意间说了句：“伙食好吃脸肿了，宿舍好住下九泉”，就被骂为“不但思想恶劣，就艺术性也是最下劣的”。给他按上“对现实不满”的帽子。关弗安同学冷天到政治课教研室去考试说了句：“这屋子冷清清的。”就被按上这是“白色恐怖思想”的帽子。……当负责人在大会上给他们戴帽子的时候，并关心地说：“我们提到这些同学的名字的时候，我们非常痛心。”好！谢谢负责人的关心！！","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"a3e9cce532","type":"paragraph","text":"五、鸿沟从那里来？","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"ecdd14ca31","type":"paragraph","text":"前面所说欧阳己的一句“牢骚”被三位一体的负责人大发雷霆后，有个积极分子说：“这是叫别个机关撵出来的。”另一个积极分子是从公安机关来的调干生，就采取公安人员的手段对付欧阳己了，他要挖欧阳己的老根，(追查欧的政治历史)并开始向欧阳己追踪了。(他举刘田德在吃饭时“偷听”他和欧阳己谈话为例)负责人得了以上那些材料，如获至宝，那就是创造典型的材料！既如此，谁还愿把自己当作他们供给材料的资本呢？还是敬鬼神而远之的好吧！","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"cf27bc009c","type":"paragraph","text":"六、正义的要求","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"1fe8df1cfa","type":"paragraph","text":"1．不信任提五名选五名的班委。2．用直接无记名投票方式改选班委。3．要求党员、团员、群众共同参与管理全班工作，处理全班事务。4．尊重群众，倾听群众的呼声。我们不是表决机器，反对“提五名——选五名”的独裁方式。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"b83c190765","type":"subtitle","text":"矫枉必须过正    中文系一年级 奈何(欧阳己)","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"9404dcba3d","type":"paragraph","text":"先生；少爷们骂我们野蛮过份了。天知道，我们只搞点小小民主，还说过火了呢？谁知道我们因为不是党团员，衣服破了，学习费用没有了，学校也不管，而且我们受过多少老爷们的闷气、迫害，有人也在深夜淌过多少眼泪。我们曾“野蛮成性的被人鞭笞”，曾“过份的受过侮辱”。我的乖少爷！让我们谈谈你们长久以来的“文明事迹”和“不过份”的行为有什么不可以呢！子曰：“矫枉必须过正，不过正不足以矫枉。”(图略)","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"fddc910386","type":"subtitle","text":"所谓人身攻击　　中文系一年级 奈何(欧阳己)","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"5699733c11","type":"paragraph","text":"有几位道学先生，也是党员老爷，他们看不惯群众的低级作品，以“反对人身攻击”为名，毁辱群众墙报。我要说：“人身攻击”总比“人权侵犯”好多了。比如学生科私审学生和将女同学的相片涂口红玩，(按：请参阅“控诉书”一文的编者按。)别人已叫退回像片，竟敢于现在还公然不理，这又是什么攻击。“老爷们，为什么你们对此不啃(吭)气”——啊！明白了，你们是“特殊材料”构成的，怎会同情得了这些群众呢！可是，我们这群落后者是支持一切大胆诉说苦情的。我建议大家有苦尽诉，大胆的实事求是的揭发宗派主义及各式的压在群众头上的老爷们。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"e83b6fc3d6","type":"subtitle","text":"问天  　　中文系一年级  奈何(欧阳己)","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"fa97660d36","type":"paragraph","text":"1．群众述说自己的劳绩，就自高自大，可耻，而党员偏要说成是特殊材料构成？“光荣”？(按：光字原来就是倒写的)何也？","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"8d84324a8d","type":"paragraph","text":"2．“谁养活了谁”。有些人说：我等赐恩，解放了群众。动辄骂群众忘恩忘本，荣耶？耻也？妄自尊大耶？小视群众耶？","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"b79bbdaa4c","type":"paragraph","text":"3．民主大些好？小些好？什么先贤哲学词典上有“紧松性”民主？(紧——指集中；松——指民主)人民有权要求完全民主否？(人民)","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"44b0b29ac0","type":"paragraph","text":"4．极端民主和自由主义罪列几等？","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"feac7b55b2","type":"subtitle","text":"流浪记 　　中文系一年级  王立名","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"a376426b3d","type":"paragraph","text":"云南大学，","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"38e8950675","type":"paragraph","text":"翠湖边坐。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"a3fcca53df","type":"paragraph","text":"高楼千堦，","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"e34e915f7a","type":"paragraph","text":"真是巍峨。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"145f3202a9","type":"paragraph","text":"十五教室，","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"3a7e6cf818","type":"paragraph","text":"暗暗淡淡，","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"0650135a48","type":"paragraph","text":"没有微光，","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"3b33a49724","type":"paragraph","text":"只有垄断。","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"4c2cee78e8","type":"paragraph","text":"“落后”群众，","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"d460c1a63d","type":"paragraph","text":"遭到分化，","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"4dc622d1df","type":"paragraph","text":"拉拉打打；","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"4d9083729a","type":"paragraph","text":"善良群众，","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"1ef8bc1499","type":"paragraph","text":"从此遭殃。","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"cf3f1875d2","type":"paragraph","text":"孤孤独独，","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"b3495cdb5a","type":"paragraph","text":"悲悲惨惨。","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"5e69d30725","type":"paragraph","text":"从此开始了：","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"4ffa766dc0","type":"paragraph","text":"到处流浪，","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"03275d41cd","type":"paragraph","text":"到处流浪。","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"32c12e3e59","type":"paragraph","text":"坚持真理，","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"4f14384709","type":"paragraph","text":"暂忍欺凌，","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"19ee8e9d06","type":"paragraph","text":"天角天涯，","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"6d57592aaa","type":"paragraph","text":"他都走遍。","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"d9909cd7c4","type":"paragraph","text":"专横独夫，","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"ad9cb6f4e0","type":"paragraph","text":"更为嚣张，","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"0bbba15fd9","type":"paragraph","text":"加紧排挤，","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"bdadeefb39","type":"paragraph","text":"捧上陷下。","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"886477b89b","type":"paragraph","text":"辱骂群众，","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"9864b6f851","type":"paragraph","text":"“白色思想”，","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"fdc53dd627","type":"paragraph","text":"“民主人士”，","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"73f39317b8","type":"paragraph","text":"大大帽儿，","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"5f2f8b9260","type":"paragraph","text":"无翼飞来。","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"7c5953a2b0","type":"paragraph","text":"自由民主，","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"7beae004af","type":"paragraph","text":"实为虚构。","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"693b64db80","type":"paragraph","text":"顺夫者生，","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"dc7dc3b400","type":"paragraph","text":"逆夫者亡。","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"89a13ca679","type":"paragraph","text":"啊——","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"41e5dc39fb","type":"paragraph","text":"东方升起了太阳，","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"d5252a51ff","type":"paragraph","text":"北京发出了巨响。","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"05b9ad1a46","type":"paragraph","text":"百家争鸣，","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"fd8d9069c3","type":"paragraph","text":"百花齐放。","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"b4baf66110","type":"paragraph","text":"啊——","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"6f1bd3c539","type":"paragraph","text":"受屈小民，","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"43b186e91c","type":"paragraph","text":"有冤要伸。","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"2ece27bfa7","type":"paragraph","text":"大鸣大放，","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"b1ff4fa3eb","type":"paragraph","text":"还要大争。","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"acb3c41a01","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席呀！","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"b4bf224e5b","type":"paragraph","text":"给给公裁，","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"9addafb2ab","type":"paragraph","text":"专横独夫，","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"7eb7c2554f","type":"paragraph","text":"从此完蛋。","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"42c504b276","type":"paragraph","text":"愿今以后，","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"f7f7a07d55","type":"paragraph","text":"阳光普照。","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"c002f8ffcc","type":"paragraph","text":"小小民主，","index":79,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"89e734d48c","type":"paragraph","text":"万世永生。","index":80,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"},{"id":"7c729a80d1","type":"paragraph","text":"注：独夫者，乃我班三位一体之执政者也。","index":81,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7"}],"page":{"id":"ef3298bc0d","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4f82db98a7","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}